dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Tassajara quadrangle, Contra Costa & Alameda Counties, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Tassajara, CA1953, AMS 1659 IV SE - Series V895, PHOTOREVISED 1968, PHOTOINSPECTED 1968."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
